  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">chromatic metal</span>, generated by fusion in the heart of a star.<br><br>This Copper has been activated by the extreme conditions in which it was formed, and is highly valuable.<br><br>Copper is found on planets orbiting <span class=\"name name-catalyst\">yellow stars</span>, and can be placed in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> to create purified <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Chromatic Metal</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>在恒星的中心融合产生。<br><br>该铜已在其所形成的极端条件下激活，并具有极高的价值。<br><br>铜可在环绕<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">黄色恒星</span>的行星上发现，可以放在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中制造出纯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>在恒星的中心融合产生。<br><br>该铜已在其所形成的极端条件下激活，并具有极高的价值。<br><br>铜可在环绕<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">黄色恒星</span>的行星上发现，可以放在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中制造出纯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>，恆星中心熔合時生成。<br><br>這種銅生成時已被當下的極端環境活化，非常珍貴。<br><br>銅可見於環繞<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">黃色恆星</span>的星球，可放入<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>製成純化<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>。"
  },
